Name: "Munchie-More” Bun
AttributesDescription: Grants 10% ATK and 20% Crit. DMG to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A Startorch Academy cafeteria classic. It looks like a simple carb-on-carb combo, but it’s surprisingly addictive: a soft bun brushed with salad dressing, stuffed with sweet-and-savory fried noodles, topped with red pickled ginger for balance. Most people can’t stop munching more.
